uidance for people and as clear proofs of true guidance and distinction (between the right and the wrong). and it has come to its end; Therefore, I seek the protection of Your Noble Face against that the sun sets on this day Or dawn rises to put end to this night But I am still liable for a sin or an offense and You want to punish me for it on the day when I will meet You.", "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": "اَللّٰهُمَّ هٰذَا شَهْرُ رَمَضَانَ الَّذِيْ اَنْزَلْتَ فِيْهِ الْقُرْآنَ هُدًى لِلنَّاسِ وَبَيِّنَاتٍ مِّنَ الْهُدٰى وَالْفُرْقَانِ وَقَدْ تَصَرَّمَ، فَاَعُوْذُ بِوَجْهِكَ الْكَرِيْمِ اَنْ تَغِيْبَ الشَّمْسُ مِنْ هٰذَا الْيَوْمِ، اَوْ يَطْلُعَ الْفَجْرُ مِنْ هٰذِهِ اللَّيْلَةِ، وَلَكَ قِبَلِيْ ذَنْبٌ اَوْ تَبِعَةٌ، تُرِيْدُ اَنْ تُعَذِّبَنِيْ عَلَيْهَا يَوْمَ اَلْقَاكَ۔", "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": null, "ArabicGreenSign12": null, "ArabicRedSign12": null, "ArabicBlueSign12": null, "Arab